title: {anime} Keitai Shoujo ep. 1-5 (batch)
description:
I could not download ALL the episodes of this great anime via torrents,
I got these from eMule, so I thought many people would highly appreciate
the possibility to download ALL episodes of this short anime via torrents.

Some anime sites say this anime has 6 episodes, and they last for 90 mins,
but some say it containes only 5 Calls, and they are about 43 mins only...
I was looking all over the net for the 6th DVD special episode, but I could
not find it... and the episodes are extremely short, only 7 mins with
opening and ending >.<#   I am not 110% sure that these are the full length
of the episodes... but as I saw from the net, these ARE...
In case you find the 6th DVD Special episode, or longer episodes than 7 mins,
plese help us, and DO make a comment here where to get them... arigatou
